My guess is they'll probably start out like bards in terms of melee ability, but only able to wear leather level armor. However Verant will introduce all new sorts of &quot;beasts&quot; in the new world, and the Beastlords will be able to transform into these new beasts and gain different abilities/strengths/weaknesses. <br>
