However to be able to become these different creatures they'll have to go thru quests to find the guy who gives them this ability to transform into a certain animal. And the separate animal forms can grow stronger with skill but can only be trained thru transforming into that animal. And there will be a transform skill that lessens the amount of time it takes before the beastlord can transform again.<br>
<br>
